promethus and grafana -- 
   System / Server / App
        ↓
   Exporter Node Exporter / Windows Exporter
        ↓
     Prometheus collects & stores metrics
        ↓
      Grafana visualizes metrics

      Why locals?
locals are just calculated values inside Terraform to avoid repeating logic

all values including secrets are usually passed via variables.tf + *.tfvars

